Package edu.nyu.cs.javagit.client

Interface Summary
IClient An interface to represent a git client type, such as a command-line client.
IGitAdd An interface to represent the git-add command.
IGitBranch An interface to represent the git-branch command.
IGitCheckout An interface to represent the <git-checkout> command.
IGitCommit An interface to represent the git-commit command.
IGitDiff An interface to represent the git-diff command.
IGitGrep An interface to represent the git-grep command.
IGitLog An interface to represent the git log command.
IGitMv An interface to represent the git-mv command.
IGitReset An interface to represent the git-reset command.
IGitRevert An interface to represent the git-revert command.
IGitRm An interface implementing functionality of the git-rm command.
IGitShow An interface to represent the git-show command.
IGitStatus An interface to represent the <git-status> command.
 

Class Summary
ClientManager This class manages the IClient instances of the various ClientTypes.
GitAddResponseImpl Class implementing GitAddResponse for setting values in it.
GitBranchResponseImpl Implementation of a GitBranchResponse.
GitCheckoutResponseImpl This class implements GitCheckoutResponse by setting values in GitCheckoutResponse.
GitCommitResponseImpl Implementation of a GitCommitResponse.
GitMvResponseImpl Implementation of a GitMvResponse.
GitResetResponseImpl Implementation of a GitResetResponse abstract class.
GitRmResponseImpl Implementation of GitRmResponse that includes setter methods for all fields.
GitStatusResponseImpl Implementation of a GitStatusResponse.
 

Enum Summary
ClientManager.ClientType
